{
  "stem": "17135.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We expected the-- the war would last a year, and then we will release.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We will be deported.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We'll be sent back to-- to Israel, to Palestine, what have you. 15 minutes after this SS officer told us, the bullies came in, about either six or eight SS guards-- so to speak, lower sergeants, corporals.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They called it blockfuhrer, rapportfuhrer, all kinds of fuhrer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Everyone had the name 'fuhrer.' And they said, so in order that you get acquainted with the spirit of Sachsenhausen, we will make some sport.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "By the way, it was already October, and there was snow already.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We-- around the-- the-- the entrance, there was-- they called it the appellplatz, a giant-- like a parade ground, where every morning they took roll call, where all the barracks had to march up in blocks and were counted and then they they reported to a rapportfuhrer that everybody's there.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Every morning and every night they counted everybody.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They want to know that nobody fled.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyway, the bullies come in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Let's make sports.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] My God.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I can't even tell you what-- what kind of sport this was.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was murder.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They let old people on-- in the cold snow roll on, and they were trampling on the people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and they had even arms with them, rifles, and they're beating it up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this was going on at least for half an hour.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, it-- it's-- they called it sport.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Everything was deliberately with deception called a name.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Like-- like they called, for example, the-- the destruction of the Jews the Endlosung-- the solution, so to speak.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were beating us up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was utterly unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And-- and you had to be very quick-- I was young-- to-- to evade.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
